content: I have seen Madonna on this tour in 5 cities: NY City, Vegas, Los Angeles, Tampa and Miami....I wish I could be there for this concert too! She is the forever queen of pop! Anything the Beyonce's, Taylor's or Gaga's do is because of Madonna!
